  "description": "The image depicts a dramatic sunset over a body of water, framed by dark silhouetted trees. The sky is ablaze with vibrant colors, transitioning from deep reds and oranges near the horizon to lighter hues of pink and purple higher up. A bridge spans the water, illuminated with a string of lights, and appears to connect to a distant city skyline. The water is relatively calm, reflecting some of the sky's colors. The trees act as a natural frame, creating a sense of depth and drawing the viewer's eye towards the sunset and bridge. There's a small boat visible on the water.",
